blogs.title: AN ACCOUNT OF RIVER ENCROACHMENT SCENARIO IN THE HIMALAYAN TOWNS OF INDIA
blogs.excerpt: Rivers are the backbone of human existence as for centuries various great civilizations have sprung up on the banks of rivers like Nile, Amazon, and Indus.
